{"tid":1668672,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新文宣方向 求下你地入嚟幫下我推","createTime":"2019-10-22T06:21:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-22T06:57:24.000Z","uid":232728,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"cb97fecba2882bd2a2ac68d479cedb0dbef97829","tid":1668672,"uid":232728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T06:21:16.000Z","msg":"尋晚太夜開 冇人睇 而家再開<br />\n11月24號係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>區議會選舉</strong></span>嘅日子。<br />\n無論政府會唔會改期，區議會選舉都係一個<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">非常重要嘅本土戰場</span></strong>，所以希望各位手足都抽啲時間睇呢篇文。如果真係唔想睇就碌到底啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n正如上面所講，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">淨番1個月多啲</span></strong>就到區議會選舉，我地要好好利用呢1個月去幫自己打贏呢條戰線。小弟希望咁多位手足係呢1個月可以撥出小小時間一齊做<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>選舉文宣</strong></span>。<br />\n小弟認為選舉文宣可以分成兩大類：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1. 推廣民主派</span></strong></span><br />\n希望咁多位手足可以宣傳下自己嗰區有邊啲<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>民主派候選人</strong></span>。<br />\n如果嗰候選人有番咁上下資歷，可能做緊<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>社區主任</strong></span>或者<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>做過議員</strong></span>又或者<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">做緊議員</span></strong>嘅，就講下佢地嘅<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>政績</strong></span>、為嗰社區做過啲咩等等。如果唔係嘅，可能係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>新人</strong></span>嚟嘅，就盡量幫佢地宣傳下，講下佢地嘅<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>背景</strong></span>呀，講下<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">有邊個幫佢地站台</span></strong>等等。如果有為當區做過嘢嘅，就當然要寫出嚟啦~~<br />\n不過如果遇到一啲獨立候選人就一定一定要check清楚，大家都知有唔少聲稱獨立嘅人其實係建制派嚟，當然亦有民主派架喇，唔好冤枉好人就得！<br />\n小弟不才，冇乜藝術細胞，只可以提供啲資料同內容大綱比大家。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hkfactcheck.io/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkfactcheck.io%2F&d=kAMrkm0lh8tAzahNx%2FKaSE2FGjryiJR74P7%2B0uEOyUg%3D&h=0e165b6a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hkfactcheck.io/</a><br />\n呢嗰網有各選區嘅候選人亦都有清楚列明係建制派定民主派。如果咁多位手足有更好嘅網，歡迎開心share~~~<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jC1FH1J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjC1FH1J.jpg&h=b618f828&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n另外，由於小弟南區人就用番南區做例子，呢嗰po就係一個好示範，share自己嗰區嘅民主派候選人比更多人睇。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2. 建制派政績</span></span></strong><br />\n除咗要宣傳自己友，都要幫對家宣傳下嘅。可以提番身邊啲街坊<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對家係任期內做咗啲咩好事</span></strong>。比啲例子大家：<br />\n<br />\n例子1. <br />\n香港仔區議員任葆琳小姐有一個傳說，就係係任期內<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">只見過任小姐1-3次</span></strong>，其餘時間就唔知去咗邊。公平啲講句，任小姐都有政績嘅，分別係成功係香港仔爭取更多圍欄，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">成功阻礙區內居民過馬路</span></strong>、成功趕走巴士線，比晒自己友進智公交啲小巴做啦，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">成功爭取區內居民交通費上升</span></strong>咁囉、<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">成功爭取監控鏡頭</span></strong>，話要打擊亂抛垃圾喎。大家就可以宣傳對家嘅政績比其他街坊知。<br />\n<br />\n例子2.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CwAfwVr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCwAfwVr.jpg&h=47ee8b3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n對家搞到<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>民生議題討論唔到</strong></span>，唔知班街坊點諗喇<br />\n<br />\n例子3.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jD3pqfK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjD3pqfK.jpg&h=a9f06463&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n對家<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>撐送中引發呢場運動</strong></span>，最後收唔到科，又唔知班街坊點諗。<br />\n<br />\n以上就係選舉文宣兩大方向，希望大家可以幫手做呢啲文宣，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>share上去social media</strong></span>, fb ,ig , twitter都要見到。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">善用Hashtag</span></strong>：<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>#一票不投建制派</strong></span><br />\n英文嘅話，小弟暫時淨係諗到<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>#SayNoToProBeijingCamp</strong></span><br />\n希望有手足諗到嗰好啲嘅hashtag再share上嚟。<br />\n除咗social media，希望當區嘅<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">連儂牆或者深藍區嘅牆上</span></strong>都會見到，比多啲人知，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">突破同溫層</span></strong>。不過，希望手足係深藍區做文宣嘅時候，一定一定要<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">注意安全</span></strong>，唔希望再有手足因為派文宣或者貼文宣而受傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nTLDR 懶人包: 做選舉文宣呀，推廣民主派同宣傳建制派做過嘅「好事」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>光復香港 時代革命<br />\n香港人 反抗！</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"bbca90fa68eb61b8382c081bd69d9f89eee9eb96","tid":1668672,"uid":232728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T06:21:33.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"a0eec9ceffa0c45dde9b3962f92be7325a6ec5e8","tid":1668672,"uid":232728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T06:21:44.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"5e4b66513ba1961132a00ca84413b5baba3e27f9","tid":1668672,"uid":232728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T06:21:55.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"d41e22230531889b539c7328b2a3a9c67f89ce5b","tid":1668672,"uid":113784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T06:22:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c14b14a926fc60a2e9adef15773d5d62f109c2e6","tid":1668672,"uid":232728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T06:22:07.000Z","msg":"搵人入嚟斷下我"},{"pid":"3f7a07c78ac00ddf06725a2ec0d630c7d2abe9ae","tid":1668672,"uid":232728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T06:22:18.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"d3d270260280fc7bed0734a05e9957b6d8689615","tid":1668672,"uid":232728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d41e22230531889b539c7328b2a3a9c67f89ce5b","tid":1668672,"uid":113784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T06:22:05.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T06:22:28.000Z","msg":"多謝手足"},{"pid":"3069398c4d9dafd9afb9ef647be4b89e5aae3e28","tid":1668672,"uid":232728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T06:22:38.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"f378492b98dbc13fd6a2db79c4eb35119950f3ba","tid":1668672,"uid":232728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T06:22:48.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"136e52db4bcada1103c5e8aa88beb379e7534b31","tid":1668672,"uid":232728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T06:23:02.000Z","msg":"唔好得我自high好冇先"},{"pid":"bea09458e36d7bf5fdc299dc353dd016fae09e7f","tid":1668672,"uid":9665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T06:23:20.000Z","msg":"推爆佢"},{"pid":"28dd9ca60d57575fb9bc234e40000df019c9b544","tid":1668672,"uid":232728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bea09458e36d7bf5fdc299dc353dd016fae09e7f","tid":1668672,"uid":9665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T06:23:20.000Z","msg":"推爆佢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T06:23:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />多謝你"},{"pid":"dac6c9a06f9fa91e972547e44bcf7f56888110bb","tid":1668672,"uid":232728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T06:23:57.000Z","msg":"7/10"},{"pid":"9214fc95dd76637e6376b232289b24c0a3e78ec0","tid":1668672,"uid":232728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T06:24:07.000Z","msg":"8/10"},{"pid":"a55a081ccf2bdb1cedbc83beae099a48a134363f","tid":1668672,"uid":232728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T06:24:17.000Z","msg":"9/10"},{"pid":"74466f096050379bdeb613c1f66d2ffe8aebb10d","tid":1668672,"uid":60751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T06:24:18.000Z","msg":"幫下你推"},{"pid":"89cb2ce3f8c7b54bbbd5c37af6ab9858c2e308c0","tid":1668672,"uid":232728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T06:24:28.000Z","msg":"10/10"},{"pid":"cbc5965dd62fb80625aca34ddc791f75cde337d8","tid":1668672,"uid":232728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"74466f096050379bdeb613c1f66d2ffe8aebb10d","tid":1668672,"uid":60751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T06:24:18.000Z","msg":"幫下你推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T06:24:41.000Z","msg":"多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38bf05eb4e0c8c8c52e69de8a50b88629bd0ed23","tid":1668672,"uid":311198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T06:25:05.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"3fcd14792e5f66c2fabc1c18438b4cb5f3b887d8","tid":1668672,"uid":249646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T06:25:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rg4zNwn.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frg4zNwn.gif&h=9e9fb2f4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"692442c8a6c0512b20c820436a3901e907b33983","tid":1668672,"uid":38931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T06:25:36.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b6786515025bee15dd0aa4cc16b4e028fa5e243d","tid":1668672,"uid":173334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T06:25:45.000Z","msg":"班撚樣冇助選團呀? 又想食人血饅頭"},{"pid":"30efcf97ab1ce701d379cd1cdb1ea97b9b85880b","tid":1668672,"uid":263147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T06:26:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hCUTiDk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhCUTiDk.jpg&h=a5cf9a44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gezTiDm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgezTiDm.jpg&h=4c0af794&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rSPDuK1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrSPDuK1.jpg&h=b5d5280b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uF2d242.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuF2d242.jpg&h=e636fd7c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"194387e62d9700d5bdba71eddab1d3545860e6b7","tid":1668672,"uid":268123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T06:26:35.000Z","msg":"【香城施政報告2019】群策群力 轉危為機<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656908\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656908</a><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>政治問題</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 重塑公民身分戶口政策保障國家、香港安全和利益<br />\n- 取消18區區議會、建立地域市政議會<br />\n- 禁止公務人員在任前、任內和任後獲港外榮典<br />\n- 改善高鐵一地兩檢操作方式<br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>便民基建</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 修正港鐵、巴士可加可減機制<br />\n- 完善機場集體運輸並加強機場、港珠澳大橋協同發展<br />\n- 興建東鐵、西鐵快速線並完善輕鐵和西鐵聯乘關係<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V1VCzpw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV1VCzpw.jpg&h=7b29ce56&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RYt8F4w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRYt8F4w.jpg&h=eecde813&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>醫療、教育方向</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 以減少送院為目標的社區護理服務<br />\n- 重塑教育, 著重知識、技能層次分工<br />\n- 興建至少四所新區域全科醫院<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B2D8F34.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB2D8F34.png&h=cb82275f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n求正評及幫推！"}]}